<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2013-01-01</DATELINE><TITLE>A unique host defense pathway: TRIF mediates both antiviral and antibacterial immune responses</TITLE><BODY>Both anti-viral and anti-bacterial host defense mechanisms involve TRIF signaling. TRIF provides early clearance of pathogens and coordination of a local inflammatory ensemble through an interferon cascade, while it may trigger organ damage. The multipotentiality of TRIF-mediated immune machinery may direct the fate of our continuous battle with microbes.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>